text: Donald Hill–Eley is an American football coach and former player. He ss the head football coach at Alabama State University. A graduate of Virginia Union University, Hill-Eley's coaching career has spanned three decades, includes stints in the Canadian Football League (CFL) and as head football coach at Morgan State University from 2002 to 2013. ==Head coaching record== ==Notes== ==References== ==External links== * Alabama State profile Category:Year of birth missing (living people) Category:Living people Category:Alabama State Hornets football coaches Category:Baltimore Stallions coaches Category:Hampton Pirates football coaches Category:Morgan State Bears football coaches Category:Norfolk State Spartans football coaches Category:Toronto Argonauts coaches Category:Virginia Union Panthers football coaches Category:Virginia Union Panthers football players Category:African-American coaches of American football Category:African-American players of American football
